`InterlockedIncrementRelease`
-
`InterlockedIncrementRelease64`


The `Interlocked…` functions provide a simple mechanism to synchronize access to data that is shared by multiple → Windows/development/process/thread[threads].

  In source file
code {
#include <winnt.h>

extern volatile long gCounter;

InterlockedIncrement(&gCounter);
code }
